data.description: Large home built in 1989.  5 bedrooms 3 full baths.  Two primary bedrooms. One could be a mother-in-law suite.  Home needs foundation work and         updating.  Lots of storage space. Kitchen has pull out drawers in cabinets. This home could be a beauty, backyard has 16 x 20 workshop with half bath and electric.  Buyers or buyer's agent should verify schools and all measurements including sq footage.
